I enjoyed the first TD more due to simplicity and replayability but this version has so many improvements that the two are barely comparable. An easy 5 stars for both games and a huge thank you to Limbic for making the best TD games on android.
The best tower game in the market.

The game is funny,  but sometimes the same aliens behave differently from one map to the next,  which doesn't make sense. Also,  the overheating in the desert modes is a plague,  it really ruins the entire experience. Remove that and it'd be 4 stars though.
A good solid tower defense game
Enjoying the game so far...I'll play a while longer to get a better feel for a review.

Good fun, simple to play and graphically pleasing. Can you ask for more considering its free?

Great game but needs more maps and more things to spend wool on, only OK for the price right now due to so few maps. I do like it more than the original. Edit: lowered my review to 2 stars since it is clear the game with receive no more updates and there are still very few maps. At the current price that I paid I would probably skip it and go with BTD5 unless you really love TD games.

column9: It's the best and most challenging tower defense game ever! I loved it!!

Addictive! I like a lot of strategy games and this one has caught my attention. The only reason I gave it 4 instead of 5 stars is it doesn't have a catchy tune as the version I played on iPhone did.

Seemingly a good game - until you reach the point where it starts randomizing the entry points of the waves. Seriously, in a tower defense game the whole point is figuring out the optimal strategy to counter the enemies and planning/building accordingly. That's not possible when randomness is introduced.
5 stars if there's a new update (more maps, new enemies etc).
Good way to pass the time
Fun and exciting game. Huge improvement from the first one. Keep u the good work guys
